ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: I would most certainly recommend this course and instructor to fellow students (in fact, I have already done so) on one hand due to the distinguishing competencies of Prof. Cleary as pedagogue and on the other hand because of his broad professional competencies which go beyond Anglophone literature.
Yes, wonderful course with a great teacher, but is a heavy workload.
